345
00:29:02,490 --> 00:29:05,010
You two should check
if your personal effects are intact.

346
00:29:05,010 --> 00:29:08,300
That's right. This happens
on the Azure Vein Society's territory.

347
00:29:08,300 --> 00:29:11,210
Our leader will intervene.

348
00:29:11,210 --> 00:29:12,930
