354
00:29:28,060 --> 00:29:30,140
Is this perhaps a premeditated ruse?

355
00:29:30,140 --> 00:29:33,010
Han, Daoist Qing Wen is known for his heroic deeds

356
00:29:33,010 --> 00:29:35,270
