357
00:29:35,270 --> 00:29:37,550
We have not suffered any losses.

358
00:29:37,550 --> 00:29:39,340
Let's just move on.

359
00:29:39,340 --> 00:29:40,650
Everything's fine.

360
00:29:40,650 --> 00:29:42,090
Let's go, Han.

361
00:29:43,310 --> 00:29:45,140
Give back the pouch.

362
00:29:48,170 --> 00:29:49,300
Thank you.

363
00:29:49,300 --> 00:29:54,750
My friends, Wu Jiu Zhi is mischievous, but he bears no ill intention.

364
00:29:54,750 --> 00:29:58,440
If he did offend you, I apologize on his behalf.

365
00:29:58,440 --> 00:30:01,010
