376
00:30:27,620 --> 00:30:32,060
Grandmaster, Miss Ru Yan from the Yan Clan Stronghold is here.

377
00:30:37,210 --> 00:30:38,780
I'm Yan Ru Yan of the Yan Clan Stronghold.

378
00:30:38,780 --> 00:30:41,150
Greetings, Grandmaster Nangong.

379
00:30:42,490 --> 00:30:46,470
I was told you brought a lot of guards
to Tainan with you.

380
00:30:47,010 --> 00:30:50,820
Grandmaster Nangong, while I can't speak for other prestigious families,

381
00:30:50,820 --> 00:30:53,640
