386
00:31:07,300 --> 00:31:10,860
We found this next to a dead rogue cultivator.

387
00:31:10,860 --> 00:31:12,880
Grandmaster Nangong, a female attendant of mine

388
00:31:12,880 --> 00:31:16,100
had her token stolen since we entered Tainan.

389
00:31:16,100 --> 00:31:18,630
Someone is obviously trying to frame me.

390
00:31:27,380 --> 00:31:29,620
Have you decided on which sect to join?

391
00:31:29,620 --> 00:31:31,910
