Spirit Beast Mountain many times.

392
00:31:31,910 --> 00:31:34,300
But I prefer the Moonshadow Sect.

393
00:31:34,300 --> 00:31:36,710
You have better taste than your grandfather.

394
00:31:37,900 --> 00:31:39,210
All right. You may return.

395
00:31:39,210 --> 00:31:41,840
Be prepared for the trials tomorrow.

396
00:31:44,920 --> 00:31:48,670
Grandmaster, judging from those brash rogue cultivators just now,

397
00:31:48,670 --> 00:31:50,820
they were clearly manipulated by someone else.

398
00:31:50,820 --> 00:31:53,250
Yet Yan Clan Stronghold
does not make enemies often.

399
00:31:53,250 --> 00:31:57,180
Do you know who is trying to frame us?

400
00:31:57,690 --> 00:32:01,740
In my opinion, Yan Clan Stronghold is not the only target.

401
00:32:01,740 --> 00:32:05,540
Your behavior does not
merely represent your family,

402
00:32:05,540 --> 00:32:08,490
but also other clan disciples like you.

403
00:32:08,490 --> 00:32:10,690
Someone is trying to exacerbate the divide

404
00:32:10,690 --> 00:32:13,430
between the clan disciples and rogue cultivators.f

