00:32:59,830 --> 00:33:01,060
This is a map of the Yue Kingdom.

417
00:33:01,060 --> 00:33:05,060
I chanced upon this map and found it intriguing.

418
00:33:05,060 --> 00:33:08,200
You can find all seven sects on it.

419
00:33:08,200 --> 00:33:09,580
- That's the Moonshadow Sect.
- That's the Spirit Beast Mountain.

420
00:33:09,580 --> 00:33:11,250
- That's the Saber-Shearing Sect.
- That's the Clear Void Sect.

421
00:33:11,250 --> 00:33:13,440
- Skyfort Castle.
- That's the Yellow Maple Valley.

422
00:33:13,440 --> 00:33:14,920
That's the Giant Sword Sect.

423
00:33:14,920 --> 00:33:18,010
These seven cultivating sects are generally abbreviated as the seven sects.

424
00:33:18,010 --> 00:33:21,340
They survived a fierce battle 1,000 years ago
in the Yue Kingdom.

425
00:33:21,340 --> 00:33:23,894
Then, where is Yan Clan Stronghold?

426
00:33:23,894 --> 00:33:25,100
Yan Clan Stronghold.

427
00:33:25,100 --> 00:33:26,620
Here. That's the Yan Clan Stronghold.

428
00:33:26,620 --> 00:33:28,640
- Yes.
- That's right.

429
00:33:28,640 --> 00:33:31,400
Then, where do rogue cultivators belong?

430
00:33:31,400 --> 00:33:33,420
We...

431
00:33:35,650 --> 00:33:37,930
We're not on this map.

432
00:33:37,930 --> 00:33:41,250
I might even say that we won't have a place in the Yue Kingdom either.

433
00:33:41,250 --> 00:33:42,350
Enough, Qing Wen.

434
00:33:42,350 --> 00:33:45,310
We brought them here to discuss the trials.

435
00:33:45,310 --> 00:33:47,130
Why bring this up?

436
00:33:47,820 --> 00:33:49,060
I'm sorry.

437
00:33:49,060 --> 00:33:51,600
Some rogue cultivators have gone missing lately.

438
00:33:51,600 --> 00:33:54,740
- Some are also left stranded...
- Qing Wen.

439
00:33:54,740 --> 00:33:56,868
What are they trying to achieve?

440
00:33:56,868 --> 00:33:59,879
They never finish their sentence, and that only diverts more attention to them.

441
00:33:59,879 --> 00:34:01,111
We're cultivating as well.

442
00:34:01,111 --> 00:34:05,492
How come some were born with access to so many resources,

443
00:34:05,492 --> 00:34:09,900
while we have to risk our lives
for a Foundation Pill?

444
00:34:09,900 --> 00:34:11,300
- Exactly.
- That's unfair.

445
00:34:11,300 --> 00:34:13,180
A Foundation Pill?

446
00:34:14,380 --> 00:34:16,140
What is that?

447
00:34:16,140 --> 00:34:17,780
You cannot not know this.

448
00:34:17,780 --> 00:34:18,610
A Foundation Pill

449
00:34:18,610 --> 00:34:20,550
can help a cultivator
to get to the Foundation Establishment Stage

450
00:34:20,550 --> 00:34:23,450
from the Qi Refining Stage.

451
00:34:23,450 --> 00:34:25,220
Qi Refining Stage?

452
00:34:26,604 --> 00:34:28,325
Which stage am I in?

453
00:34:28,325 --> 00:34:32,230
If you're just starting out, you're in the Qi Refining Stage.

454
00:34:36,000 --> 00:34:37,160
And then?

455
00:34:37,160 --> 00:34:38,750
Listen carefully.

456
00:34:38,750 --> 00:34:39,960
In the world of cultivation,

457
00:34:39,960 --> 00:34:41,480
all stages can be divided into

458
00:34:41,480 --> 00:34:44,880
lower level, middle level, and upper level.

459
00:34:44,880 --> 00:34:46,370
The lower level stages include

460
00:34:46,370 --> 00:34:48,480
the Qi Refining
Stage, the Foundation Establishment Stage,

461
00:34:48,480 --> 00:34:49,920
the Core Formation Stage,
the Nascent Soul Stage,

462
00:34:49,920 --> 00:34:51,200
and the Spirit Transformation Stage.

463
00:34:51,200 --> 00:34:54,270
The middle level stages
are the Void Refining Stage,

464
00:34:54,270 --> 00:34:56,210
the Body Unity Stage, and
the Great Ascension Stage.

465
00:34:56,210 --> 00:34:59,900
The upper level stage only has the Tribulation Transcendence Stage.

466
00:34:59,900 --> 00:35:01,550
If you ascend from this stage,

467
00:35:01,550 --> 00:35:04,180
you can become an immortal
and live as long as the universe.

468
00:35:05,050 --> 00:35:06,480
But these are just myths.

469
00:35:06,480 --> 00:35:09,570
No one has seen anyone
above the Nascent Soul Stage.

470
00:35:10,760 --> 00:35:14,515
Is it very difficult to get a Foundation Pill?

471
00:35:15,240 --> 00:35:17,250
It's not just difficult to get one.

472
00:35:17,250 --> 00:35:20,690
The pill determines the fate of a cultivator,

473
00:35:20,690 --> 00:35:24,720
and by extension, the future of a sect.

474
00:35:24,720 --> 00:35:26,860
Therefore, in the past, the seven sects

475
00:35:26,860 --> 00:35:30,330
and the prestigious families
had a monopoly over the pills.

476
00:35:30,980 --> 00:35:32,940
They have all the pills.

477
00:35:34,240 --> 00:35:36,780
Until the trials came along.

478
00:35:37,590 --> 00:35:41,830
Han, at a glance, the trials give you a chance

479
00:35:41,830 --> 00:35:44,110
to enter the seven sects.

480
00:35:44,110 --> 00:35:47,370
But in reality, everyone is after the pills.

481
00:35:48,400 --> 00:35:50,920
500 years ago, a veteran rogue cultivator

482
00:35:50,920 --> 00:35:52,510
gathered thousands of other rogue cultivators

483
00:35:52,510 --> 00:35:54,280
to negotiate with the seven sects.

484
00:35:54,280 --> 00:35:56,130
Thanks to them,
we now have a chance to compete fairly

485
00:35:56,130 --> 00:36:00,050
against disciples of prestigious clans
to enter the seven sects.

486
00:36:00,050 --> 00:36:02,820
And as a result, we also become their enemies.

487
00:36:02,820 --> 00:36:03,970
But let's be frank.

488
00:36:03,970 --> 00:36:06,050
We rogue cultivators
do not have access to many things.

489
00:36:06,050 --> 00:36:07,220
And those who hail from a prestigious clan

490
00:36:07,220 --> 00:36:09,550
can feed their disciples with tons of elixirs.

491
00:36:09,550 --> 00:36:11,700
- How is this fair?
- Yes, that's not fair.

492
00:36:11,700 --> 00:36:13,740
Uneven distribution of resources.

493
00:36:13,740 --> 00:36:17,660
No wonder they hate the clan disciples.

494
00:36:18,800 --> 00:36:21,000
Have you found anything
about the rogue cultivators?

495
00:36:21,000 --> 00:36:23,860
Several men are following
the core members as we speak.

496
00:36:23,860 --> 00:36:26,110
The leader is a man called Qing Wen.

497
00:36:26,110 --> 00:36:28,340
He has only attained Tier 11
of the Qi Refining Stage,

498
00:36:28,340 --> 00:36:30,510
but he is a great speaker.

499
00:36:30,510 --> 00:36:33,630
He has many followers among the rogue cultivators.

500
00:36:33,630 --> 00:36:34,900
Keep a close eye on him.

501
00:36:34,900 --> 00:36:37,590
Let me know if anything happens.

502
00:36:37,590 --> 00:36:39,010
Yes.

503
00:36:41,480 --> 00:36:44,970
My friends, the seven sects will put us through two trials.

504
00:36:44,970 --> 00:36:47,300
The first one is the spirit root trial tomorrow.

505
00:36:47,300 --> 00:36:50,880
The second one is the Tianwu Arena trial tomorrow.

506
00:36:50,880 --> 00:36:53,360
The Tianwu Arena trial is very dangerous.

507
00:36:53,360 --> 00:36:58,120
Therefore, we must secure a spot in tomorrow's trial first.

508
00:36:58,120 --> 00:36:59,340
A spirit root

509
00:36:59,340 --> 00:37:02,670
comes in five elements:
Metal, wood, water, fire, and earth.

510
00:37:02,670 --> 00:37:04,560
- You know it already.
- Metal, wood, water, fire, .

511
00:37:04,560 --> 00:37:05,720
- and earth.
- Mortals do not have a spirit root

512
00:37:05,720 --> 00:37:06,800
so they cannot cultivate.

513
00:37:06,800 --> 00:37:10,320
The more spirit roots you have,
the worse you progress.

514
00:37:10,320 --> 00:37:13,360
Those who have four or five spirit root elements

515
00:37:13,360 --> 00:37:16,610
can sense the spiritual aura around us.

516
00:37:16,610 --> 00:37:21,220
Yet they can only reach Tier Three or Tier Four in their lives at most.

517
00:37:21,220 --> 00:37:23,620
We call this a fake spirit root.

518
00:37:23,620 --> 00:37:25,300
- Fake spirit root?
- Fake spirit root?

519
00:37:25,300 --> 00:37:27,980
Those who have two or three spirit root elements

520
00:37:27,980 --> 00:37:30,970
have a true spirit root.

521
00:37:30,970 --> 00:37:33,860
Sir, what if the spirit root
comes with only one element?

522
00:37:33,860 --> 00:37:36,450
Then, it is an exceptionally rare
heavenly spirit root.

523
00:37:36,450 --> 00:37:39,920
A cultivator with that gift
has earned the favor of the maker.

524
00:37:39,920 --> 00:37:42,660
His progress will defy comprehension.

525
00:37:43,697 --> 00:37:47,300
I see. Cultivation is deeply tied to one's talent.

526
00:37:47,300 --> 00:37:49,110
In that case, do I have a true spirit root

527
00:37:49,110 --> 00:37:51,200
or a fake spirit root?

528
00:37:51,200 --> 00:37:53,380
Physician Mo never told me.

529
00:37:57,150 --> 00:37:59,490
I hope I have the heavenly spirit root.

530
00:37:59,490 --> 00:38:02,330
There are only limited spots for those who wish to enroll in the seven sects

531
00:38:02,330 --> 00:38:03,930
through the spirit root trial.

532
00:38:03,930 --> 00:38:05,530
People from the prestigious clan

533
00:38:05,530 --> 00:38:09,670
will do what they can to take our spots
in the seven sects.

534
00:38:09,670 --> 00:38:11,740
They wish to impede our cultivation.

535
00:38:15,800 --> 00:38:19,890
So, power speaks the loudest
in the cultivation world.

536
00:38:23,440 --> 00:38:25,450
Tier 1 to Tier 13.

537
00:38:26,230 --> 00:38:28,610
It is the complete set of Longevity Art.

538
00:38:32,150 --> 00:38:33,710
Interested?

539
00:38:34,840 --> 00:38:36,010
Pay up.

540
00:38:36,010 --> 00:38:37,890
- How much?
- Nine gems.

541
00:38:39,030 --> 00:38:40,230
Nine gems?

542
00:38:40,230 --> 00:38:41,720
That's too expensive.

543
00:38:43,590 --> 00:38:45,450
Tier Ten of the Qi Refining Stage?

544
00:38:45,450 --> 00:38:46,930
Now you've seen what I can do.

545
00:38:46,930 --> 00:38:48,700
Pay up.

546
00:38:52,710 --> 00:38:56,180
Little girl, I do want to buy this book.

547
00:38:56,180 --> 00:38:58,280
But nine gems is too expensive.

548
00:38:58,280 --> 00:38:59,670
Can I ask for a better price?

549
00:38:59,670 --> 00:39:01,220
How much are you offering?

550
00:39:02,030 --> 00:39:03,660
Two?

551
00:39:05,400 --> 00:39:08,840
Da. Er. San. Si.

552
00:39:08,840 --> 00:39:10,660
Come!

553
00:39:11,440 --> 00:39:12,760
Is this the guy?

554
00:39:12,760 --> 00:39:14,450
That's right.

555
00:39:14,450 --> 00:39:17,030
He read our book but refused to pay.

556
00:39:17,030 --> 00:39:18,020
I'm selling it for nine gems.

557
00:39:18,020 --> 00:39:19,500
But he only offered two.

558
00:39:20,770 --> 00:39:23,360
What in the daylight robbery!

559
00:39:23,360 --> 00:39:24,140
What?

560
00:39:24,140 --> 00:39:26,665
How did you know we were robbers
before we started cultivating?

561
00:39:26,665 --> 00:39:28,016
- How did you know?
- How did you know?

562
00:39:28,016 --> 00:39:29,880
We quit many years ago.

563
00:39:29,880 --> 00:39:32,800
- How did you know?
- Speak up.

564
00:39:32,800 --> 00:39:38,740
Everyone, this sign means two strengthening pills

565
00:39:38,740 --> 00:39:40,410
