566
00:39:40,410 --> 00:39:42,010
What do you think?

567
00:39:52,000 --> 00:39:53,880
Give me the book.

568
00:40:05,030 --> 00:40:07,170
Stand there. You can't leave.

569
00:40:12,280 --> 00:40:13,710
I gave you the pills.

570
00:40:13,710 --> 00:40:15,340
What else do you want?

571
00:40:15,340 --> 00:40:19,560
- Your pills...
- You overpaid.

572
00:40:19,560 --> 00:40:21,340
- Yes.
- Yes.

573
00:40:21,340 --> 00:40:23,680
You can have the Longevity Art book.

574
00:40:24,480 --> 00:40:28,170
This mega mystic pouch is a gift for you as well.

575
00:40:31,030 --> 00:40:32,790
It's a gift.

576
00:40:37,030 --> 00:40:40,540
The Five Mengs are righteous!

577
00:40:42,070 --> 00:40:45,360
Indeed, indeed. Farewell.

578
00:40:46,840 --> 00:40:47,880
No need to see me off!

579
00:40:47,880 --> 00:40:49,400
No need!

580
00:40:54,760 --> 00:40:57,951
The pills are more useful than gems.

581
00:40:57,951 --> 00:41:00,936
Lucky for me, I brought extra when I left
Shenshou Valley.

582
00:41:01,630 --> 00:41:04,610
And now, I also have a mystic pouch.

583
00:41:04,610 --> 00:41:07,470
I no longer have to bring many bags with me.

584
00:41:09,280 --> 00:41:10,780
For your fragment of a magic item,

585
00:41:10,780 --> 00:41:12,180
I'll buy it for five low-grade gems.

586
00:41:12,180 --> 00:41:13,300
