591
00:41:18,820 --> 00:41:22,280
What can it do exactly?

592
00:41:22,280 --> 00:41:23,840
It's very useful.

593
00:41:24,920 --> 00:41:26,380
Look.

594
00:41:26,880 --> 00:41:28,400
I...

595
00:41:28,400 --> 00:41:32,650
I can use that fragment
