596
00:41:36,400 --> 00:41:38,050
It is a fragment of a magic item, all right.

597
00:41:38,050 --> 00:41:40,780
But it's too small.

598
00:41:40,780 --> 00:41:41,970
You know what?

599
00:41:41,970 --> 00:41:44,060
Given you also have a cute face,

600
00:41:44,060 --> 00:41:47,540
I will offer one strengthening pill.

601
00:41:48,280 --> 00:41:49,260
Mister Lu,

602
00:41:49,260 --> 00:41:50,970
