603
00:41:50,970 --> 00:41:52,300
I offer six gems.

604
00:41:52,300 --> 00:41:53,590
Can I have it?

605
00:41:53,590 --> 00:41:55,550
I offer seven gems.

606
00:41:55,550 --> 00:41:56,710
Eight gems.

607
00:41:56,710 --> 00:41:59,050
Okay. Eight gems, it is.

608
00:42:01,590 --> 00:42:02,660
Sorry.

609
00:42:02,660 --> 00:42:03,920
I was just joking around.

610
00:42:03,920 --> 00:42:06,020
Me too.

611
00:42:06,020 --> 00:42:10,000
Besides, Miss. Your fragment
truly isn't worth that much.

612
00:42:19,000 --> 00:42:21,180
Miss. Don't go.

613
00:42:21,180 --> 00:42:22,990
They don't want it, but I do.

614
00:42:22,990 --> 00:42:24,180
One gem.

615
00:42:24,180 --> 00:42:25,860
I offer one gem.

616
00:42:25,860 --> 00:42:27,930
I'm asking for seven gems.

617
00:42:27,930 --> 00:42:31,280
All of you... Is anyone else interested?

618
00:42:34,570 --> 00:42:37,260
I don't think anyone else is bidding.

619
00:42:37,260 --> 00:42:38,880
Anyone?

620
00:42:39,880 --> 00:42:41,410
Two vials of Golden Marrow Pill

621
00:42:41,410 --> 00:42:43,483
