622
00:42:43,483 --> 00:42:45,940
Please don't tell me you're joking around too.

623
00:42:59,030 --> 00:43:00,530
Deal.

624
00:43:10,920 --> 00:43:13,360
My friend, why are you doing this?

625
00:43:13,360 --> 00:43:15,300
You ruined my negotiation for no reason at all.

626
00:43:15,300 --> 00:43:17,170
You think you can leave?

627
00:43:19,710 --> 00:43:23,930
But I bought this fragment with a fair price.

628
00:43:23,930 --> 00:43:25,820
Isn't this a fair trade?

629
00:43:25,820 --> 00:43:26,860
Fine.

630
00:43:26,860 --> 00:43:30,620
Let me teach you what fairness means.

